2011-07-07T00:23:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/mediatek-inc-june-sales-fall-17-68-table-2454-tt.html
MEDIATEK INC (2454)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 17.68% to NT$3,976,841,000 from NT$4,830,957,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales           3,976,841        4,830,957   
YOY%             -17.68%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           24,711,015       39,169,206  
YOY%             -36.91% 
=================================================================
 